Both methods manipulate the ResultSet, with hasNext() checking the state of the ResultSet and remove() modifying it by deleting the current row.
The toArray method in BasicRowProcessor is used by the next() method to convert a row into an Object[], indicating a dependency on the ResultSet processing logic.
